main event: A civilian couple observed a circular, pearly iridescent object hovering and spinning while playing golf in Kenya.
interesting points: The object emitted a high-pitched buzzing sound similar to a swarm of bees., The couple observed the object hovering about 100 feet above them., When they called out to a nearby individual, the object took off rapidly at a steep angle., The object's size was compared to a 20 cents piece from East Africa., It was described as having a smooth surface without any protuberances.
sighted object: a circular, pearly iridescent flying saucer
witness description: a man and his wife who were playing golf
